========
Full Installation Guide:

*) Check if this is the lastest version before you run any script:
   http://code.google.com/p/iredmail/downloads/list

*) Please do read the installation guide before you run any script
   shipped within iRedMail:

   - Red Hat Enterprise Linux 5 & CentOS 5:
     http://code.google.com/p/iredmail/wiki/Installation

   - Debian 5.x
     http://code.google.com/p/iredmail/wiki/Installation_on_Debian

   - Ubuntu 8.04 & 9.04
     http://code.google.com/p/iredmail/wiki/Installation_on_Ubuntu

   - OpenSuSE 11.3
     http://code.google.com/p/iredmail/wiki/Installation_on_OpenSuSE

   - FreeBSD 7.2 & 8.0
     http://code.google.com/p/iredmail/wiki/Installation_on_FreeBSD

